p.k: Party On / On Your Toes / Friend Wars / The Scratch Pack As Zoe preps Cleo LeBall's birthday party, Axel and the team run damage control against a jealous crasher. / After a Porcupunk sighting Axel leads a recon mission that slowly but surely proves to be a wild goose chase devised by Sarge. / Princess SugarSalt dupes Axel into hanging out with Cleo LeBall and usurps his role as team leader forcing Zoe to step in and keep the toys together. / Axel and the team must run damage control after a loose spark of Minergy accidentally turns Zoe's old toys - a set of cute squishy kittens - into a pack of snarling beasts.
